{"tid":2264513,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[fb要人]素食公司登廣告不含中資被小粉紅圍剿","createTime":"2020-10-30T16:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T19:42:13.000Z","uid":321932,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"da0ba9edfaaa9530910218dbe525014dfe4500d1","tid":2264513,"uid":321932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n6nvDs4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn6nvDs4.jpg&h=3d687e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/flowlikethesea/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fflowlikethesea%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=9edd6eea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/flowlikethesea/</a><br />\n瑞典小記 Flow Like the Sea<br />\n18小時 &middot; <br />\n最新消息1: Peas of Heaven 收起左原本在Facebook個道歉聲明，早幾日佢地被好多強國人留下負評，搞到Review好低分，宜家連Review都唔俾，不過大家可以繼續去like佢地個page! <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/peasofheaven\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpeasofheaven&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=9be8f989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/peasofheaven</a><br />\n最新消息2: 好多真香港人睇到之後都問香港有無得買Peas of Heaven的良心食品，啱啱問過佢地，香港就暫時未有，不過好有興趣推去香港賣! 佢地好想知有咩途徑，如果有黃公司有興趣，都歡迎直接同佢地聯絡!<br />\n瑞典素食公司廣告稱﹕產品不含中國投資者 <br />\n惹強國人不滿﹕ 歧!視!中!國!人!<br />\n近日(10月26日)一間著名瑞典素食食品製造商Peas of Heaven<br />\n在首都斯德哥爾摩Stockholm 展示一系列最新廣告，廣告的內容係:<br />\nInget K&ouml;tt. Inga &auml;gg. <br />\nInga Kinesiska Investerare.<br />\nInget Gluten.<br />\n中文翻譯:<br />\n無肉，無雞蛋<br />\n無中國投資者<br />\n無麩質<br />\n呢個廣告一出，真係不得了，一群強國人玻璃心又碎到一地都係。間公司立即接到來自四方八面的投訴，話呢個廣告係 歧!視!中!國!人! 兩日之後公司被迫跪低，收返個廣告，亦都同受影響人士道歉。但係一班小粉紅又點會就咁算數，繼續去Peas of Heaven的Facebook聲討佢地。<br />\n其實拒絕同某國做生意，在瑞典又豈止得Peas of Heaven一間公司。有另一間瑞典著名的牛仔褲公司，都講明唔會在某國設廠製造牛仔褲，因為呢間公司投資前會檢視該國的民主人權狀況，一定要達佢地的標準，先會考慮設廠。<br />\n某國人覺得被人地歧!視!都已經唔係第一次，今年10 月頭先就一單。話說瑞典斯德哥爾摩一家餐廳貼左張海報，海報上面的維尼被畫成「蝙蝠人」，又引起一班人的暇想，話係歧!視! 中!國!人! 歧視在瑞典呢D著重自由平等的國家，係好嚴重的指控，所以間餐廳最終都係跪低，撕走海報。<br />\n如果大家都想支持下瑞典呢D是非黑白分明的公司，大家不妨去佢地Facebook留個言，在瑞典住的真香港人，今個星期記得去超市買份素食支持下!<br />\nPeas of Heaven聲明(公司已收回此聲明)﹕<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/&hellip;/a.5223932982377&hellip;/1089559064854536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fa.5223932982377%E2%80%A6%2F1089559064854536&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=f73d4d8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/&hellip;/a.5223932982377&hellip;/1089559064854536</a><br />\n瑞典蝙蝠人事件回帶﹕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/flowlikethesea/posts/1012956815843120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fflowlikethesea%2Fposts%2F1012956815843120&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=ae8256c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/flowlikethesea/posts/1012956815843120</a>"},{"pid":"0520da1bfae0e2dc310f3764b2dcdec7c3e2ff23","tid":2264513,"uid":138144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CGppHzxpUqP/?igshid=nm35c20214n7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCGppHzxpUqP%2F%3Figshid%3Dnm35c20214n7&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=f292be9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCGppHzxpUqP%2F%3Figshid%3Dnm35c20214n7&h=f018af91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CGppHzxpUqP/?igshid=nm35c20214n7</a><br />\n蝙蝠雜種artist 個ig 入去支持瑞典手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4a29b318ed98940e798441827b70bd95d4b548","tid":2264513,"uid":301631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:45:37.000Z","msg":"tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\